# Files that don't need to be in the build context for the API image.
# Build context is the `backend/` directory; trim everything that's
# OS-specific build output or unrelated to `dotnet restore` / `publish`.

**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/*.user
**/TestResults/
**/.attachments/
**/coverage*/
**/*.log
